                            <comment id="16418742" author="msahyoun" created="Thu, 29 Mar 2018 10:44:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=chdeul&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;chdeul&quot;&gt;chdeul&lt;/a&gt; I&apos;ve adjusted the logic for check if a translation is needed. Could you verify if it works for you?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16422021" author="chdeul" created="Mon, 2 Apr 2018 08:36:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have test the trunk version : it&apos;s &lt;b&gt;Ok&lt;/b&gt; on my little test.&lt;/p&gt;

